00:06:49.079 --> 00:06:54.079
Now, during that time, will we need to fear the natural elements?

00:06:54.079 --> 00:06:55.079
Not at all.

00:06:55.079 --> 00:06:58.079
Second Peter chapter 2 verse 9 assures us,

00:06:58.079 --> 00:07:04.079
Jehovah knows how to rescue people of godly devotion out of trial.

00:07:04.079 --> 00:07:10.550
Jehovah will perfectly control the natural elements so his people are not harmed.

00:07:10.550 --> 00:07:16.550
This knowledge about the awesome power of wind and water should make us powerful by faith.

00:07:16.550 --> 00:07:21.550
It should build our faith not only in Jehovah's ability to protect us in the future,

00:07:21.550 --> 00:07:24.550
