00:07:30.550 --> 00:07:35.550
The one who controls the storehouses of the wind and hail is our helper.

00:07:35.550 --> 00:07:38.550
According to Hebrews chapter 13 verse 6,

00:07:38.550 --> 00:07:41.550
we do not need to be afraid.

00:07:41.550 --> 00:07:50.550
That's true now, and it will be true in the future when Jehovah brings the natural elements at his disposal against our enemies.

00:07:50.550 --> 00:07:54.550
